content: Data import from {{organizationName}} Workspace to {{organizationName}} {{productName}} is complete!

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a message indicating that data import from an organization's Workspace has been completed successfully. It appears in the UI as part of a data import process, specifically on a completion step or button, and includes placeholders for the product name and organization name.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Arabic translation reverses the order of 'organizationName' and 'productName'. The English says 'Data import from {{organizationName}} Workspace to {{productName}} {{organizationName}}'. The Arabic translation, as written, implies the product is within the workspace.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: اكتمل استيراد البيانات من مساحة عمل {{organizationName}} إلى {{productName}} {{organizationName}}!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The placement of 'organizationName' at the end of the Arabic sentence feels unnatural and disrupts the flow. While technically a direct translation, it's not stylistically ideal.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: اكتمل استيراد البيانات من مساحة عمل {{organizationName}} إلى {{productName}} التابعة لـ {{organizationName}}!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Czech translation uses 'do' instead of 'do' (into) which feels slightly less natural when referring to a process moving data into a system. While understandable, it can be improved.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Import dat z {{organizationName}} Workspace do {{organizationName}} {{productName}} je dokončen! -> Import dat z {{organizationName}} Workspace do {{organizationName}} {{productName}} je kompletní!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Greek translation retains the double curly braces {{ }} which are meant for placeholders and should be removed.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Remove the double curly braces from the Greek translation.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The colon after '{{organizationName}}' is unnecessary and disrupts the flow. It's better to omit it.
The Armenian translation uses a hyphen (-) instead of a space after 'Workspace'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Տվյալների ներմուծումը {{organizationName}} Workspace ից {{organizationName}} {{productName}} ավարտված է:

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'Worskspace' is misspelled. It should be 'Workspace'.
The Portuguese translation uses 'A importação' which is grammatically incorrect. It should be 'A importação de'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A importação de dados do {{organizationName}} Workspace para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} foi concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'A importação de dados...' should be 'A importação dos dados...' The preposition 'de' implies 'of', while 'dos' correctly indicates 'of the' when referring to data (plural).
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A importação dos dados do {{organizationName}} Workspace para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} foi concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Sinhala translation 'ආනයනය සම්පූර්ණයි!' is a literal translation of 'import is complete'. A more natural and idiomatic phrasing would be 'මිපදවා ගැනීම් අවසන්' (mipadawa gatim avasan) or something similar that conveys the meaning of 'import completed'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: {{organizationName}} Workspace සිට {{organizationName}} {{productName}} වෙත දත්ත මිපදවා ගැනීම් අවසන්!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The use of `{{organizationName}}` and `{{productName}}` is consistent with the English content, but ensure that these variables are properly handled during rendering in Sinhala environments.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Ensure proper variable substitution for `{{organizationName}}` and `{{productName}}` during rendering.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'Увоз' is potentially incorrect. 'Увоз' can mean 'import' but in this context 'Увожење' might be more suitable for a more formal tone, reflecting a completed process.
